<div class="container-fluid page-header py-5 mb-5">
    <h1 class="text-center text-white display-6">About Us</h1>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-5 align-items-center mb-5">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <img src="/img/hero-img-2.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded w-100" alt="Fruitables farm">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h4 class="text-secondary mb-2">Our Story</h4>
                <h1 class="mb-4 text-primary">Fresh, Organic, and Local</h1>
                <p>
                    Fruitables started with a simple idea: bring fresh, organic fruits and vegetables
                    from local farms across Pakistan straight to your table, without the middlemen and
                    without the markup. We work directly with growers in Punjab and Sindh to make sure
                    every crate that reaches you was picked at its best.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Today we deliver to homes and businesses across the country, backed by a simple
                    promise: quality produce, fair prices, and fast delivery - every single order.
                </p>
                <div class="row g-3 mt-3">
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <h3 class="text-primary mb-0"><%= productCount %>+</h3>
                        <p class="mb-0 text-muted">Products available</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <h3 class="text-primary mb-0">1963+</h3>
                        <p class="mb-0 text-muted">Happy customers</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4 text-center">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="bg-light rounded p-4 h-100">
                    <i class="fas fa-seedling fa-2x text-primary mb-3"></i>
                    <h5>Sourced Locally</h5>
                    <p class="mb-0 text-muted">Direct from farms in Lahore, Multan, and Karachi.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="bg-light rounded p-4 h-100">
                    <i class="fas fa-truck fa-2x text-primary mb-3"></i>
                    <h5>Fast Delivery</h5>
                    <p class="mb-0 text-muted">Same-day delivery in major cities across Pakistan.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="bg-light rounded p-4 h-100">
                    <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart fa-2x text-primary mb-3"></i>
                    <h5>Fair Prices</h5>
                    <p class="mb-0 text-muted">No middlemen markup - fair prices for growers and customers alike.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
